Iris Flower Classification using Scikit-learn

Project Overview
This project predicts the species of Iris flowers using Machine Learning. The famous Iris dataset is used to train and evaluate the classification model.

Dataset
- Iris Dataset (Scikit-learn)

Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib

Machine Learning Algorithm
- Classification using Scikit-learn

Workflow
- Data Loading
- Data Exploration
- Data Preprocessing
- Model Training
- Model Evaluation
- Prediction

Results
- Successfully classified Iris flowers into three species.
- Evaluated model accuracy using Scikit-learn metrics.

